name: Cynthia Gary
description: I am a single,never married before,I am very Outgoing, Communicative, Easy going,Outspoken, I am also a very Romantic type, Hold hands while walking, I’m trustworthy so far as people tell me maybe I’m just laid back,lolz…I also tend to have a good heart with so much of love to give and to receive.I seek for a complete honest man, who will love me, a strong man with a strong heart who will want our relationship to last forever, one with good heart and know how to handle matters, I want a lover not a fighter..
